{"tid":981301,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"點解晚餐要豐富過早餐?","createTime":"2019-01-14T08:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T09:46:42.000Z","uid":173617,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7f2c93a29693c49516538de100ace8d07ff39f98","tid":981301,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:00:30.000Z","msg":"正常起身,8個鐘無食過野,應該好肚餓,要食多d。而晚餐準備訓教,食多會un住個胃,唔舒服,究竟咁既飲食習慣點會成為主流? 商家佬諗出黎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754136258def16f6467742f4d48116cba5468fcd","tid":981301,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:04:12.000Z","msg":"DINNER唔豐富朝早仲撚餓啦"},{"pid":"05da13120ab04b798c09e7f494af43f06485ed3a","tid":981301,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:11:51.000Z","msg":"夜晚果餐最撚肚餓"},{"pid":"0d06978646e1995a1dade7cfd71bd16ad47613e9","tid":981301,"uid":159074,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:12:13.000Z","msg":"點解?<br />\n因為解錯左囉<br />\n依加講緊早餐要豐富晚上可以唔食都仲得WO"},{"pid":"fdee69fc0ac891d3b3298e10fd1b72d37ab4d42b","tid":981301,"uid":104658,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"早上吃飽、中午要吃好、晚上要吃少<br />\n<br />\n好似係咁<br />\n<br />\n如果你晚餐想食多啲應該要早啲食<br />\n<br />\n如果你十點先食完十一點就瞓好難消化"},{"pid":"b0e2e1fa9a9e33febe45808eb7421889c51ca6e0","tid":981301,"uid":173617,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:18:28.000Z","msg":"小弟6點起身,打邊爐做早餐,起碼頂到6-7個鐘,中午1點食個阿活咖喱豬,夜晚6點食麥皮或白粥。"},{"pid":"534c03dc54c2e7a4160bd69e6d77a8f679e9159c","tid":981301,"uid":44435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:24:56.000Z","msg":"聽邊個講"},{"pid":"5beee41a36d0b43b409745ce1f900c1921db8001","tid":981301,"uid":58512,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:25:46.000Z","msg":"其實最好係中午果餐豐富<br />\n早餐好似最吸收"},{"pid":"9cd9e17c854715fd875df2e42a2f4df34337e946","tid":981301,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"朝早食2個常餐=1個晚餐價錢<br />\n如早餐30蚊<br />\n午餐50蚊<br />\n晚餐70蚊<br />\n<br />\n10蚊白粥,香蕉等水果。<br />\n<br />\n早豐富晚輕食法:30+30+50+10=120<br />\n正常食法:30+50+70=150<br />\n<br />\n慳到30蚊"},{"pid":"717b00a0c76786efcd55d40318d1313aca701c8c","tid":981301,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:43:40.000Z","msg":"朝早食2個常餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952f8cb88140aba150e9bb8fb4b46b71f3f26863","tid":981301,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cd9e17c854715fd875df2e42a2f4df34337e946","tid":981301,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"朝早食2個常餐=1個晚餐價錢<br />\n如早餐30蚊<br />\n午餐50蚊<br />\n晚餐70蚊<br />\n<br />\n10蚊白粥,香蕉等水果。<br />\n<br />\n早豐富晚輕食法:30+30+50+10=120<br />\n正常食法:30+50+70=150<br />\n<br />\n慳到30蚊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"無啦啦又講咗去慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f42d15f8a1ad663175a178c57b56dea79e0112","tid":981301,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"因為多數夜晚最齊人，早餐多數一條友食，是鳩旦啦"}]}